{
  "ref": "black-eye",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "'Black-eye'",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Before Tower of Life",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What's going on?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Ah, we be building this 'ere tower. Lookin' good ain't it?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "It does look pretty impressive, but what are you doing hanging around?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Tea break, naturally."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Naturally. Not sure why I asked."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Fancy some?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Tea? Sure."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "You'll find a kettle in the box to the-"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Erm...yeah...no...sorry...gotta go."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After Tower of Life",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Say, that's a nice helmet."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Why, thanks."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I was just wondering if you might be able to help me out with one?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Always glad to help a budding builder. But first, prove your Construction knowledge by answering some questions."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "How many nails does it take to make a rocking chair?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "One?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "One? How do you suppose you'd use a single nail?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Five?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Nope. Keep guessing!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Three?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Bingo! Okay, now what takes 3 planks, 3 cloths and 3 nails to make, and helps remove light from a room?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Torn curtains?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Nice one. Last question: I like fish and I want to put some in my garden, but I need a special water feature. What materials would I require?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "8 clay pieces and 3 limestone bricks?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Oh, and you were so close!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "10 clay pieces?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "That's it! You seem to know your stuff. I got a spare helmet from a builder that died on... I mean, err, had to leave the job for greener pastures."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Greener pastures?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Fair enough."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Wait a minute! Is there blood on this helmet?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Erm, no, that's just, erm, paint. Yes, paint! That's what it is!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Oh, okay. Thanks. Bye."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Ha, gullible fool."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Nothing."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "10 limestone bricks?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Guess again."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "A brown rug?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Of course, because that's what everyone needs - a rug up at their window."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Opulent curtains?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Those curtains are not going to be in any way opulent, matey."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Thank you - just as nice as the one in your bank!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'Black-eye'",
                  "text": "Yes - just as nice as the one you're carrying I'd say."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}